c512c913b8?s=96&d=mm&r=g","contentUrl":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ca6233450e4444e1b97627c512c913b8?s=96&d=mm&r=g","caption":"Dora S."},"description":"Dora is the founder, recipe developer, and photographer at Dora's Table and Mi Mero Mole. Born and raised in Mexico and a graduate of the Culinary Institute of America in New York, she adopted a vegan (plant-based) diet to take control of her health.","sameAs":["https://dorastable.com/about/about-me/"],"url":"https://dorastable.com/author/dora-l-stonegmail-com/"},{"@context":"http://schema.org/","@type":"Recipe","name":"Almond Atole (Atole Almendrado)","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dora S."},"description":"This almond atole combines almond milk, ground almonds, cinnamon. piloncillo, and masa harina to make a warm, comforting, and sweet beverage","datePublished":"2017-11-19T17:54:36+00:00","image":["https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/atole-almendrado-4.jpg","https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/atole-almendrado-4-500x500.jpg","https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/atole-almendrado-4-500x375.jpg","https://dorastable.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/atole-almendrado-4-480x270.jpg"],"recipeYield":["4","4 servings"],"totalTime":"PT25M","recipeIngredient":["3 1/2 cups Almond milk, (unsweetened)","1 stick Ceylon cinnamon","2/3 cup Raw Almonds","1/4 cup Masa harina, (maseca)","1/2  cup Water","3  - 4 oz.  Piloncillo, ((half of a cone))","1 tsp. Ground cinnamon"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Heat almond milk in a medium sauce pot, bring to a simmer.","name":"Heat almond milk in a medium sauce pot, bring to a simmer.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"While the milk comes to a simmer, grind the almonds in your blender until they resemble a powder. Set aside.","name":"While the milk comes to a simmer, grind the almonds in your blender until they resemble a powder. Set aside.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Dissolve the masa harina in 1/2 cup of water.","name":"Dissolve the masa harina in 1/2 cup of water.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the masa harina to the almond milk, and mix well.","name":"Add the masa harina to the almond milk, and mix well.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Simmer for 5 minutes, stirring to make sure it doesn’t stick to the bottom of the pot.","name":"Simmer for 5 minutes, stirring to make sure it doesn’t stick to the bottom of the pot.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the ground almonds, cinnamon stick, and piloncillo to the saucepot. Simmer at very low heat for 6 - 8 minutes.","name":"Add the ground almonds, cinnamon stick, and piloncillo to the saucepot. Simmer at very low heat for 6 - 8 minutes.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-5"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Serve hot. Sprinkle with some ground cinnamon. As it cools it will thicken, so add more almond milk if necessary.","name":"Serve hot. Sprinkle with some ground cinnamon. As it cools it will thicken, so add more almond milk if necessary.","url":"https://dorastable.com/almond-atole-atole-almendrado/#wprm-recipe-5705-step-0-6"}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"4.1","ratingCount":"11"},"recipeCategory":["Drinks"],"recipeCuisine":["Mexican"],"keywords":"almonds, atole, mexican","nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","servingSize":"1 serving","calories":"202 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"14 g","proteinContent":"7 g","fatContent":"15 g","saturatedFatContent":"1 g","sodiumContent":"287 mg","fiberContent":"5 g","sugarContent":"2 g"